                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\"><placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName>\n                                        <date>7<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> May 5609</date>.</p>\n                              <p>My dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I avail myself of the present opportunity<lb/> to\n                                        acknowledge the receipt of your communication, and<lb/> at\n                                        the same time, to express my warm thanks for the kind<lb/>\n                                        sentiments which it breathes. Being aware how deeply at<lb/>\n                                        heart, I have the subject of our correspondence you need\n                                        no<lb/> assurance on my part, how earnestly I have taken\n                                        into<lb/> consideration the contents of your esteemed\n                                        letter. I readily<lb/> admit the desirability of being on\n                                        the spot, wherever a situation<lb/> should offer; but as you\n                                                  <add>?</add> second my situation; I shall<lb/>\n                                        briefly and openly place you in possession of my position.\n                                        The<lb/> proceeds of my labor are far from being\n                                        unremunerative, but<lb/> having a family to maintain, I\n                                        could ill spare the<lb/> expense of <sic>travelling</sic>,\n                                        without the matter being definitely<lb/> settled before\n                                        hand. I have no doubt of being able to<lb/> obtain leave of\n                                        absence from the Directors of the Hebrew National<lb/>\n                                        Institution, yet, this would but partly be of service, for I\n                                        would,<lb/> of necessity, have to relinquish many <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">private</hi> pupils, the<lb/>\n                                        emoluments arising from whom are about $200 pr ann.\n                                        This<lb/> is the sole reason which renders my repairing so\n                                                  <placeName><sic>Cincinatti</sic></placeName>,\n                                        im=<lb/>=practicable, otherwise, I would not fear the\n                                        result. The fame<lb/> remarks apply to any other situation,\n                                        if my election be left to<lb/> chance. I do not however,\n                                        relinquish the hope of obtaining<lb/> a clerical situation\n                                        in the <placeName>United States</placeName>, as I can (if\n                                        required)<lb/> procure testimonials of the most satisfactory\n                                        nature.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Since my last communication, I</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3jm2474n/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
