                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>have been elected <add>חזן</add> of the congregation <add>נוה\n                                                  שלום</add> of <placeName>Spanish\n                                        town</placeName>,<lb/> so that I am de facto as this moment,\n                                        one of the Jewish Clergy.<lb/> I think it necessary, However\n                                        to premise, that an understanding<lb/> exists that I am\n                                        thereby unfettered in accepting any other<lb/> ministerial\n                                        office. My object in responding to their call<lb/> has been\n                                        solely with the view of reorganizing the Congregation<lb/>\n                                        which, in a religious sense, has ceased to exist. The\n                                        community<lb/> are not in a position to compensate a\n                                        minister, I am therefore<lb/> compelled to retain my\n                                        situation as master of the school in<lb/>\n                                        <placeName>Kingston</placeName>, and on occasions of\n                                        Service, go to the <placeName>Spanish Town</placeName> by\n                                        the<lb/> Train the afternoon previous. You will therefore\n                                        not fail to<lb/> perceive that in this matter I have not\n                                        been influenced by<lb/> pecuniary gain. In what I have done,\n                                        I have been actuated<lb/> merely by a desire to promote the\n                                        cause of our Holy Religion,<lb/> and to remove the stigma\n                                        from a body of Israelites, having<lb/>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">two</hi> places of Worship, and neither\n                                        open for the service of the God<lb/> of\n                                                  <persName>Jacob</persName>. So far have I been\n                                        successful. The taunting question<lb/> can no longer be\n                                        uttered? <add>למה נעול בית אלוהים</add>. Under my\n                                        superintendence<lb/> a Sunday School is also about being\n                                        established, as with scarcely<lb/> an exception the younger\n                                        branches of the community are ignorant of<lb/> the very\n                                        first principles of our faith, much less of our\n                                        national<lb/> Language. Thro' the instruction I have\n                                        received from Hazan <persName>Lopes</persName><lb/> of our\n                                        city (of whom you have perhaps heard) I am enabled to<lb/>\n                                        officiate in the Portuguese Minhag, but I should,\n                                        nevertheless, prefer<lb/> being attached as Minister to a\n                                        German Congregation (<add>מנהג פולין</add>) in the<lb/>\n                                        <placeName>United States</placeName>, having had much more\n                                        experience, and being<lb/>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">perfectly</hi> an fait at the duties of\n                                        the latter. I therefore, <hi rend=\"underline\">do\n                                        not</hi><lb/> relinquish the desire of obtaining a situation\n                                        as Hazan in <placeName>America</placeName>.<lb/> May I rely\n                                        on your continued good offices in forwarding my</p>"
                  },
